column5: What exactly do you consider a whack job? Lol  I'm working this weekend, maybe another time.....but......I've been called a whack job many times  S.
I've fished with Sinker in the past and yes....he's a whack job....LOL.  Just kidding!!
Well, ccmt is the first to say it, but I'm sure there are a few more coming lol  S.
Nah..I still remember that trip...you taught me how to rip jigs through weeds for walleye!  A technique I still use today!  Oh...to keep on topic with the thread...I cant fish this weekend either.
I'm out.  I'm completely insane, and I'm fishing Long Point Bay this weekend.  Ya ever need a boat down here, mine's always got a seat.
That whack job comment was hilarious!  I can't make it out this weekend which is too bad because everyone else here it's NUTS!! LOL.  Kidding boys, couldn't resist.
